  "translations": {
    "en": "And watch your daily prayers and how you perform them, for you will be leading the people. Therefore you must fulfil all its conditions and not belittle it. Whenever an imam leads prayers with deficiency, he bears the responsibility, while the people following suffer no loss. So fulfil it and guard it – you will earn the same reward as theirs without their reward being reduced.",
